title: Prime WLA Location, Pet friendly!
posting_body: ['Located in a prime West Los Angeles neighborhood, West Park Village is a premium apartment community with two heated pools, fitness center, and a professional on-site management team.', 'A variety of floor plans provide flexible options to suit your needs, while the convenient location keeps you close to the bustling lifestyle of West Los Angeles.', '- Near public transportation', '- Located 3 miles from Santa Monica College', '- Gated parking (limited availability for Studio and Efficiency units – call to confirm)', '- After-hours courtesy patrol', '- Package Lockers', '- Dishwashers', '- 24-Hour maintenance emergency', '- Modern cabinets and countertops throughout', '- Dual pane windows throughout', '- Located 2 1/2 miles from UCLA', '- Fitness center', '- Ceiling fans', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing is subject to change.', 'Call for details.']
